ick=\"return HMTrackTopiclink(this);\" class=\"weblink\">https://www.turkiye.gov.tr/tse-kimlik-dogrulama-2336</a></span></p>\n\n</td>\n\n</tr>\n\n<tr>\n\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top; padding:6px; border:solid thin #000000;\"><p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0 0 20px 0;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Gümrük ve Ticaret Bakanlığı Trafik Şahadetnamelerinin üst yazılarının doğrulanması</span></p>\n\n</td>\n\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top; padding:6px; border:solid thin #000000;\"><p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0 0 20px 0;\">Gümrük ve Ticaret Bakanlığı</p>\n\n</td>\n\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top; padding:6px; border:solid thin #000000;\"><p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0 0 20px 0;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><a href=\"https://www.gtb.gov.tr/\" target=\"_blank\" onclick=\"return HMTrackTopiclink(this);\" class=\"weblink\">https://www.gtb.gov.tr/</a></span><br />\n\n<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><a href=\"https://e-belge.gtb.gov.tr/\" target=\"_blank\" onclick=\"return HMTrackTopiclink(this);\" class=\"weblink\" title=\"https://e-belge.gtb.gov.tr/\">https://e-belge.gtb.gov.tr/</a></span></p>\n\n</td>\n\n</tr>\n\n<tr>\n\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top; padding:6px; border:solid thin #000000;\"><p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0 0 20px 0;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px; color: #000000;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n</td>\n\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top; padding:6px; border:solid thin #000000;\"><p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0 0 20px 0;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px; color: #000000;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n</td>\n\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top; padding:6px; border:solid thin #000000;\"><p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0 0 20px 0;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px; color: #000000;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n</td>\n\n</tr>\n\n<tr>\n\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top; padding:6px; border:solid thin #000000;\"><p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0 0 20px 0;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">E-belgeleri doğrulama